<div class="mp-manage-imgload">
	<div class="mp-manage-covertitle">
		<span class="mp-manage-imgtitle">设置背景图片</span>
	</div>
	<span class="mp-manage-cover-label">封面背景图片</span>
	<div class="mp-manage-uploadbox">
		
		<div class="mp-manage-imgupload"  node-type="uploadcontainer">
			<div class="uploadbg"></div>
			<div class="privewbox">
				<img  class="previewimg"  node-type="previewimage" />
				<span class="uploadbtn">
					<span class="reuploadicon"></span><span class="reuploadiconlabel">重新上传</span>
				</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	

		<div class="mp-manage-uploadinfo">
			尺寸建议：上传的图片宽度和高比例越接近手机屏幕宽度和高度比例，展示效果越好（9:16）
			<br>
			你也可以 <a href='javascript:void(0)' class="defaultimg" node-type='defaultimg'>使用默认图片</a>
		</div>
		<input type="file" style="display:none;" node-id="fileinput" />
	</div>
</div>

<div class="mp-manage-navbg" id="mp-manage-navbgbox">
	<span class="mp-manage-cover-label">菜单背景图片</span>
	<div class="navscontainer" id="mp-manage-navupload"></div>
</div>
